{"tid":1074000,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"［捷克］布拉格獨遊","createTime":"2019-03-23T05:41:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-07T16:57:44.000Z","uid":149406,"like":32,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"cd2895b80cbe52420eb6a7f365dd5764ea3f9916","tid":1074000,"uid":149406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T05:41:54.000Z","msg":"是咁的，小弟依家喺奧地利exchange，聽朋友講布拉格非常值得去，我上網睇啲相又真係唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />趁今個weekend幾free，於是就即興係flixbus買咗張來回布拉格嘅車飛，星期六出發，星期一翻，黎個短短地嘅3日2夜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇下佢係咪真係咁正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n黎緊呢個post會直播我嘅旅程，以圖為主，文字為副<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果出文出得慢，我應該係周圍行緊，希望各位連登仔唔好屌咁大力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n事不而遲，依家係奧地利時間0624，正式出發去百塔之城！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/23/132720_ffb1dfa45ff2544dc8976927f6c450ff.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F23%2F132720_ffb1dfa45ff2544dc8976927f6c450ff.png&h=8c5bd8dc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/23/132726_8702cc375ac853e88df7bbdebe6bcb89.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F23%2F132726_8702cc375ac853e88df7bbdebe6bcb89.png&h=99bd5852&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n買撚咗flixbus，去到個站搵黎搵去都搵唔到架巴士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />劣劣地即刻問下職員我係咪去錯站，佢叫我去6號月台，我話唔係喎，我果張巴士飛黎架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />經過一輪雞同鴨講之後，原來呢程係flixbus同westbahn (奧地利鐵路公司）合作嘅，先搭火車再搭巴士，總共六粒鐘就到達布拉格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好多謝呢位地鐵叔叔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />good start出路遇貴人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係咗多先，到咗再講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74cf04a48a818db0ce94550a3f9c7feab353d897","tid":1074000,"uid":93449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T05:45:26.000Z","msg":"LM<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da999bba5db939ea4da891d451bef1cd9d8ccd45","tid":1074000,"uid":230917,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T05:45:46.000Z","msg":"不通知親友"},{"pid":"5d7dc2292186fb28cf4cedf8a9470b6bfad9e1fc","tid":1074000,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T05:46:38.000Z","msg":"布拉格 ck <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71270f9b74fa5e073ba736ecca1c0e64fbbdb7dc","tid":1074000,"uid":13514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T05:47:39.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"d55bbb59d59f906b67e56f19ed47aea6baeb1126","tid":1074000,"uid":23684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T05:53:22.000Z","msg":"幾年前去過 太多人(遊客)"},{"pid":"a94067437ceaee93dc558763dc8ac71ce436e4b4","tid":1074000,"uid":149406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da999bba5db939ea4da891d451bef1cd9d8ccd45","tid":1074000,"uid":230917,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T05:45:46.000Z","msg":"不通知親友"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T06:01:02.000Z","msg":"交低咗啲行程俾屋企人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />roommate都知道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />touch wood有咩三長兩短都有人知嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fcc108b987ece9fcbd72fafde327fb6d5a67667","tid":1074000,"uid":152009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T06:04:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cf2bb2dc8fd44d1068e25f0c99c1d1ba385c1ed","tid":1074000,"uid":173548,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T06:04:46.000Z","msg":"想去 不過條仔唔比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好羡慕巴打可以自己一個去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a033f0024f13bcf10021ba5361de61a1beba7208","tid":1074000,"uid":149406,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T07:22:02.000Z","msg":"𠵱家係朝早八點三，到達奧地利第三大城市Linz<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dw1jJO9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdw1jJO9.png&h=55136116&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n準備轉巴士去布拉格，巴士站同火車站距離唔遠，過條馬路就到了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5g5ktf1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5g5ktf1.png&h=1215945e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n想影一影個巴士站，點知對情侶一齊望曬鏡頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再搭多4個鐘巴士就到喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n瞓陣先，早抖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KauYeWJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKauYeWJ.png&h=d37d5bea&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"029c6d4c9e8c1fc0e447ae66fbaf8892e0336719","tid":1074000,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T08:47:31.000Z","msg":"留明"},{"pid":"09ac04658ec801add7b2d4340e87ce957bad7b2c","tid":1074000,"uid":172694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T09:27:42.000Z","msg":"巴士冇電視嘅？"},{"pid":"c4ae4346eddcbe243d1623174cf3df1eb7c5e467","tid":1074000,"uid":50595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T09:29:54.000Z","msg":"直接由布拉格坐flixbus去維也納唔使轉車都好似under 5個鐘"},{"pid":"39e95d0b5470579b005dfd04dbcbfe04b98103e0","tid":1074000,"uid":16697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T09:44:58.000Z","msg":"邊個位去PRAGUE?<br />\n不如直接CK SHUTTLE去CK再STUDENT AGENCY BUS去返PRAGUE,又快又平"},{"pid":"0721ff1cff9d16f61574d52af28c2e317fb7faa6","tid":1074000,"uid":149406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"39e95d0b5470579b005dfd04dbcbfe04b98103e0","tid":1074000,"uid":16697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T09:44:58.000Z","msg":"邊個位去PRAGUE?<br />\n不如直接CK SHUTTLE去CK再STUDENT AGENCY BUS去返PRAGUE,又快又平"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T13:09:47.000Z","msg":"Salzburg去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今之淨係喺prague玩兩日，下次有機會再去ck小鎮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e58f9252544a174b89d08bb15076b90827253bdb","tid":1074000,"uid":53261,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T13:22:23.000Z","msg":"建議你朝早啲時間去charles bridge 同埋個天文鐘<br />\n<br />\n可以就一天光7，8點就去<br />\n<br />\n小好多好多好多人<br />\n<br />\n條橋又未開始擺檔<br />\n<br />\n鐘又無人圍觀"},{"pid":"3bc494cb9c47925b275e1fb33d8f2d2c9d16a4a4","tid":1074000,"uid":149406,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T13:25:53.000Z","msg":"一瞓醒已經到咗prague main train station<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SfHCxrC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSfHCxrC.png&h=384302d2&s={SIZE}\" /> 天氣好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嗱嗱臨落車搵hostel放低個大背囊，去到check in原來間房未ready，不過都可以放低個啲野先，hostel都幾企理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/23/211448_26ca6f19828f08363882a430c4b19454.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F23%2F211448_26ca6f19828f08363882a430c4b19454.png&h=011ba657&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n搞掂曬啲野，就出發去唱錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />捷克雖然係歐盟入面，但佢都有自己嘅貨幣，克朗。喺條街度有好多英文唔錯嘅𡃁仔同叔叔叫你搵佢唱錢，但呢個世界邊有咁撚方便嘅野，無啦啦有人serve你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？通常佢地會收你手續費或者唱其他鳩貨幣俾你，總之就唔好隨街唱啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cdPYgWh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcdPYgWh.png&h=0f5b97e9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pqPJs23.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpqPJs23.png&h=bb4933b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上網搵到old town入面有間信譽唔錯嘅找換店，即刻狗衝去唱翻幾個錢傍身，事關我已經好肚餓喇，下晝兩點半都未食野，個身又無錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最後唱咗50歐，因為佢無手續費，所以遲下唔夠先再唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n搵野食先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個肚咕咕叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baa6202f272d9a0fab56abf1b02303cb24af587a","tid":1074000,"uid":149406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e58f9252544a174b89d08bb15076b90827253bdb","tid":1074000,"uid":53261,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T13:22:23.000Z","msg":"建議你朝早啲時間去charles bridge 同埋個天文鐘<br />\n<br />\n可以就一天光7，8點就去<br />\n<br />\n小好多好多好多人<br />\n<br />\n條橋又未開始擺檔<br />\n<br />\n鐘又無人圍觀"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T13:27:15.000Z","msg":"好呀巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你有無去圖書館果個tour?"},{"pid":"8633e213f6b73b9978d468c6ecc1a815cd011577","tid":1074000,"uid":134182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T13:51:06.000Z","msg":"屌同我完全一樣<br />\n<br />\n又係Salzburg 去Prague <br />\n一開始又係搭火車去linz<br />\n<br />\n個陣揾咗個站好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80367c145a16f8cd8c1c7522edcb46e5fbb49f4a","tid":1074000,"uid":152009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T13:52:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />羨慕"},{"pid":"d4abaf4cc80d58f90a72050e4831dcc02eefb05f","tid":1074000,"uid":136299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T14:17:13.000Z","msg":"lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"863ac5d2927989bcf485b6116fdc4c7978057307","tid":1074000,"uid":53261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"baa6202f272d9a0fab56abf1b02303cb24af587a","tid":1074000,"uid":149406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e58f9252544a174b89d08bb15076b90827253bdb","tid":1074000,"uid":53261,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T13:22:23.000Z","msg":"建議你朝早啲時間去charles bridge 同埋個天文鐘<br />\n<br />\n可以就一天光7，8點就去<br />\n<br />\n小好多好多好多人<br />\n<br />\n條橋又未開始擺檔<br />\n<br />\n鐘又無人圍觀"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T13:27:15.000Z","msg":"好呀巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你有無去圖書館果個tour?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T14:37:25.000Z","msg":"無去到呀，我都係兩日一夜同自己周圍行嚟行去渣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n特別啲係去左共產主義博物館<br />\n<br />\n其實好細但都睇左好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"953b937cbc1ea762649ebc6e20e653d81008cbd8","tid":1074000,"uid":149406,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T16:57:48.000Z","msg":"唱完錢搵咗間餐廳，見佢靚靚仔仔咁就坐低咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jikD2v0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjikD2v0.png&h=aa8c208e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7C17VQ7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7C17VQ7.png&h=3689727d&s={SIZE}\" />嗌咗杯啤酒，衰鬼又幾好飲，甜甜地咁，有淡淡嘅麥麥味。主菜就嗌咗個叫Gulas嘅牛肉加dumpling， 呢個餃子個質地似麵包溝薯仔，非常有飽肚感，加埋啲肉汁係面，成碟餸味道唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢餐夾埋都係250幾克朗，即係港幣大約90蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />小弟覺得好抵屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n食飽飽去old town兜咗個圈，見到好多中國，韓國同歐洲遊客加學生團，成個square都極多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />題外話，prague食大麻係合化嘅，成條街都係草味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我行下fing下，就去咗klementinum library，聽講係全世界最靚嘅圖書館之一，入面有600萬本書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />更加係耶蘇學會同大學嘅所在地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/08eNbrJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F08eNbrJ.png&h=595a0efa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n等緊入場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73b69f6e0e5efcf937122adadce7db0f791783e5","tid":1074000,"uid":65603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T17:02:57.000Z","msg":"Lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b025b5a54afce7c4aa9c046224205f5a2dc8d1c1","tid":1074000,"uid":169185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T17:07:42.000Z","msg":"prague 個old town真喺好靚<br />\nLM<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8159e8ae9b9502385011452987a7a54a1cdff530","tid":1074000,"uid":33497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T17:11:24.000Z","msg":"LM<br />\n<del>上次走馬看花睇少好多野</del><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccfe0b04285e779493502ef95023329d6ff75b76","tid":1074000,"uid":225116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T17:20:24.000Z","msg":"過幾日去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bf916b56ac177a59b3c532fc883195860ed73bb","tid":1074000,"uid":65603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T17:45:01.000Z","msg":"網上面又話捷克唔俾食大麻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb739c35558f4c156156d62d7e6ec2e4fee610d9","tid":1074000,"uid":21469,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T18:05:28.000Z","msg":"exchange去過覺得比人吹大左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBudapest就真心正"},{"pid":"7d870bf152cec7817d7be0289e7a736ca6ebbce3","tid":1074000,"uid":176834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da999bba5db939ea4da891d451bef1cd9d8ccd45","tid":1074000,"uid":230917,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T05:45:46.000Z","msg":"不通知親友"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T03:02:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba00f9922bd5a02828cc3aa660a3174abedbbbad","tid":1074000,"uid":220345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T05:43:31.000Z","msg":"記住要去CK"},{"pid":"d7268cbaa7fe97798d8d76873fdc931035afe185","tid":1074000,"uid":235475,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3bc494cb9c47925b275e1fb33d8f2d2c9d16a4a4","tid":1074000,"uid":149406,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T13:25:53.000Z","msg":"一瞓醒已經到咗prague main train station<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SfHCxrC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSfHCxrC.png&h=384302d2&s={SIZE}\" /> 天氣好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嗱嗱臨落車搵hostel放低個大背囊，去到check in原來間房未ready，不過都可以放低個啲野先，hostel都幾企理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/23/211448_26ca6f19828f08363882a430c4b19454.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F23%2F211448_26ca6f19828f08363882a430c4b19454.png&h=011ba657&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n搞掂曬啲野，就出發去唱錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />捷克雖然係歐盟入面，但佢都有自己嘅貨幣，克朗。喺條街度有好多英文唔錯嘅𡃁仔同叔叔叫你搵佢唱錢，但呢個世界邊有咁撚方便嘅野，無啦啦有人serve你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？通常佢地會收你手續費或者唱其他鳩貨幣俾你，總之就唔好隨街唱啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cdPYgWh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcdPYgWh.png&h=0f5b97e9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pqPJs23.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpqPJs23.png&h=bb4933b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上網搵到old town入面有間信譽唔錯嘅找換店，即刻狗衝去唱翻幾個錢傍身，事關我已經好肚餓喇，下晝兩點半都未食野，個身又無錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最後唱咗50歐，因為佢無手續費，所以遲下唔夠先再唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n搵野食先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個肚咕咕叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T06:31:33.000Z","msg":"哩間找換店可能係全布拉格最穩陣"},{"pid":"be47a89263c926b30f570e098bf7345ed233ebea","tid":1074000,"uid":235475,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ba00f9922bd5a02828cc3aa660a3174abedbbbad","tid":1074000,"uid":220345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T05:43:31.000Z","msg":"記住要去CK"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T06:32:53.000Z","msg":"其實有啲名過其實<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UzJFA0A.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUzJFA0A.png&h=55f7e196&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cb01ff26726bf01f0bb6e0e9bf96e33e0e6f36dc","tid":1074000,"uid":34148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be47a89263c926b30f570e098bf7345ed233ebea","tid":1074000,"uid":235475,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ba00f9922bd5a02828cc3aa660a3174abedbbbad","tid":1074000,"uid":220345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T05:43:31.000Z","msg":"記住要去CK"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T06:32:53.000Z","msg":"其實有啲名過其實<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UzJFA0A.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/